I would say that, we must
always keep in mind,

6
00:00:33,190 --> 00:00:34,390
that we have a soul

7
00:00:35,270 --> 00:00:37,150
and that soul can be attacked.

8
00:00:37,390 --> 00:00:40,230
It has been already
attacked when with all

9
